"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jls1665702632169.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jls1665702632169.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jls1665702632169.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jls1665702632169\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the label text for the command button is automatically updated when a new glyph is loaded. <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> (default) or <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jls1665702632169__p_d102107e1_d102108e1_d102109e1\">\n         \n                                AutoLabel\n                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code>\n</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jls1665702632169__table_d12029e1_d12030e1_d12031e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jls1665702632169__table_d12029e1_d12030e1_d12031e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jls1665702632169__table_d12029e1_d12030e1_d12031e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jls1665702632169__table_d12029e1_d12030e1_d12031e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n                     (default)</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jls1665702632169__table_d12029e1_d12030e1_d12031e1__entry__2\">Label text is taken from the character mode text\n                     for the glyph. The label text is loaded when the glyph is loaded. Associated\n                     tool tip text is not displayed, even if the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Tool Tip</span>\n                     property is set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jls1665702632169__table_d12029e1_d12030e1_d12031e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jls1665702632169__table_d12029e1_d12030e1_d12031e1__entry__2\">Label text is not changed.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jls1665702632169__section_rpv_s2t_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d538686e130\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jls1665702632169__p_d102113e1_d102114e1_d102115e1\">This property only works if the\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Representation</span> property is set to\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">Uniface</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jls1665702632169__section_mlp_v2t_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d538686e145\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jls1665702632169__pre_zkz_w2t_vwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(BTN) = \"autolabel=false\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jls1665702632169__section_al2_x2t_vwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d538686e154\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrc1665702631553.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrc1665702631553.html\" title=\"The CommandButton is a logical widget that enables a user to initiate an action by clicking the button.\">CommandButton</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/btj1665702631955.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Representation</a><p>This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613941\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613941\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Auto Label (AutoLabel) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 12, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 This property determines whether the label text for the command button is automatically updated when a new glyph is loaded. True (default) or False AutoLabel = \" True | False \" Value Description True (default) Label text is taken from the character mode text for the glyph. The label text is loaded when the glyph is loaded. Associated tool tip text is not displayed, even if the Tool Tip property is set to True . False Label text is not changed. Description This property only works if the Representation property is set to Uniface . Example: Setting in ProcScript $fieldproperties(BTN) = \"autolabel=false\" Copy Applies To CommandButton Related Links Representation This property determines the appearance of the command button when running on the Microsoft Windows operating system (XP and later versions). One of Windows (default), Uniface, or Header. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}